title: Sankalan 2024
description: Sankalan is the illustrious annual fest organized by the Department of Computer Science, University of Delhi. Embarking on its 20th voyage, this two-day extravaganza epitomizes a diverse array of technical marvels and non-technical wonders to discover. It beckons both seasoned experts and newcomers to share in its brilliance. From riveting coding competitions to captivating artistic events, Sankalan offers everyone a platform to showcase their talents and explore the frontiers of technology and art.
